commit.message:
Set library version

This allows distributions to split out development files properly
to a -dev package. The resulting library now gets named
"libkeyfinder.so.2.2.4" with symlinks to "libkeyfinder.so.2" and
"libkeyfinder.so". This also allows packagers to more easily track
updates that requires rebuilding or updates of mixxx
